| comment "Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2025-5252 — Recovery Inhibition (incransom)"
| comment "Status: experimental | Level: high | ID: ff371eb9-ddad-5dbd-9a4b-ac0cf5c52dc4"
index=* sourcetype=endpoint*
| where (CommandLine="*recoveryenabled no*" OR CommandLine="*bootstatuspolicy ignoreallfailures*") AND (process="*\bcdedit.exe")
